                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vois les pontificats étendre, sur l’opprobre\nDes noces, leur chasuble aux violets d’octobre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Les cieux clament les De Profundis irrités",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Et les Dies iræ sur les Nativités.",
